# Gittan source-collector changes

If you are adding or editing a collector under **`collectors/`**, before treating
the work as done:

1. In **Cursor**, run **`/gittan-source-collector`** with the diff or `@` files
   attached, **or** open and follow **`docs/skills/gittan-source-collector.md`**
   (same workflow).
2. Pick the **source role** from `docs/specs/source-evidence-policy.md` first — a
   collector is evidence, not truth by itself.
3. Make `collector_status` distinguish disabled / missing-prereq / zero-event /
   events / error; add a doctor row; keep tests on fixtures (no live user data).

Canonical contract: **`docs/specs/source-collector-contract.md`**. Policy:
**`AGENTS.md`**.
